As far as the damage..I am of the contention that all the Epics should be FAR supperior to anything else in the game..and should be very difficult to obtain..So I would have to disagree that the stats should be near the Lance of Thunder or anything that drops on a killable mob..The Tunare sword is rediculous in it's strength..I would suggest that the sword be like 65/45 with a bane of 10% + to undead creatures..I would also have some sort of clickable spell providing a LOH to other players that would reset every 1/2 hr or so..The 150 stun is really a joke..I would prefer to have some kind of group healing proc (300hp-500hp heal), thus making those grping with us want to group with us..<br>
to me the EPIC is what makes EQ a true Quest game with end results and coupled with the AA stuff it is very fun..<br>
